{"id": 852, "genre": 1001, "title": "你对现在的直播app有什么要说的？", "description": "从吃饭直播到海淘直播什么都有的，当代社会。", "record_count": 2870, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183736elrihJat6uYECDR3.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-03-10T11:22:36Z", "options": [{"id": 57088, "content": "不靠谱 没感觉", "image": "img/option/option/2016060614483904IoZ5hBugavbc1w.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 511102}, {"id": 58112, "content": "多读书多看报少吃零食多睡觉?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 504131}, {"id": 57089, "content": "都是一群无聊的人凑到一起去看直播，大多是看脸我就能盯一天。反正到现在为止 我是没看到过一些有意义的直播", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 511104}, {"id": 58118, "content": "网络直播需要整顿。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 515262}, {"id": 57095, "content": "这也能看", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241704}, {"id": 57351, "content": "如果用来做新闻现场的直播，会有多少人看？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 512784}, {"id": 55560, "content": "妖魔鬼怪太多 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 208, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 57097, "content": "极度浪费时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416250}, {"id": 55562, "content": "打赏功能鼓励乱来 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 47, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 57098, "content": "如果说打开直播页面，看到的都是锥子脸、一字眉、大美瞳、操着一口音律极重的憨嗓、哼着跑调儿的所谓的歌，那直播的人有那么几个就够了，也不是非要琴棋书画样样精通，能放松能给播友们带来欢乐是最好不过的。不一定每天都会有新鲜的故事发生，哪怕就只是直播身边的流浪小猫小狗，给它们喂一点吃哒，留个周围的地址，或许会有附近的有爱心的人看到。不是说要多矫情，自然的让人看着舒服的", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 479829}, {"id": 55563, "content": "炫耀自己无聊的生活也不会变有趣 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 377, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 58636, "content": "原来真的可以靠脸挣钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 514965}, {"id": 57101, "content": "个性，别魔性，就行", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 499760}, {"id": 57102, "content": "不懂", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 354783}, {"id": 58126, "content": "空虚的人看寂寞的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 467049}, {"id": 57103, "content": "都是无聊的没内涵的在看脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 487739}, {"id": 57104, "content": "街上的捞b都换场子卖骚了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 402734}, {"id": 57872, "content": "边缘地带产业", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 500021}, {"id": 58129, "content": "都是作业太少了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 515621}, {"id": 57107, "content": "睡觉都有人看 这人类是有多无聊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 511179}, {"id": 57108, "content": "反正我没看过除了吃播以外的……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 459273}, {"id": 64020, "content": "中国第一位YouTuber：Http://youtube.com/littlebigchinabysean，喜欢看视频的去支持一下吧！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 543836}, {"id": 57109, "content": "想告诉你我喜欢你但是明明知道不可能", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 511189}, {"id": 57110, "content": "vvvg", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 511210}, {"id": 58390, "content": "多穿衣服", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 213076}, {"id": 57111, "content": "哈哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 511210}, {"id": 57112, "content": "我没有胸 也没有大长腿。有我也不去。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 511130}, {"id": 57115, "content": "怀着好奇心一探究竟，参与者绝大部分是年轻人，甚至未成年，而他们的表现也让人无比震惊。疾速前行的中国，天真的以为孩子们都过上了幸福的生活，但是精神上的空虚已然证明了我们的失误。总理的政府工作报告依然将教育投入的增长放在倒数，如果继续，无论是否取代美帝，终有一天，国家会葬送在几十年后“他们”的手上。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 453060}, {"id": 57116, "content": "我就想知道那些天天化妆直播卖萌的妹子到底为什么不用上学", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 319909}, {"id": 57117, "content": "存在即合理，但很多直播本身并没有意义ಠ_ಠ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 507242}, {"id": 57118, "content": "感觉像青楼女子/男子 搔首弄姿 摇尾乞怜", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147051}, {"id": 57630, "content": "别作了，省点电", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 487404}, {"id": 57119, "content": "除了会读评论还会干嘛？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 427917}, {"id": 57120, "content": "直播什么都好说，只求不在朋友圈刷屏，没人想看你，真的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 231266}, {"id": 57121, "content": "不成熟。很多都卖脸，没有独特的手机直播魅力，和良好的直播体验。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360615}, {"id": 57633, "content": "然而网上的骗子越来越多，防不胜防", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 506521}, {"id": 57122, "content": "想看也没流量", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 127272}, {"id": 57123, "content": "卖肉卖节操的时代", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 406151}, {"id": 57124, "content": "没有自己的生活，才去围观他人的生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 228493}, {"id": 57636, "content": "一群空虚的人围观一个空虚的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 513741}, {"id": 57125, "content": "哪裡給他們的自信⋯", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 130398}, {"id": 57126, "content": "哪裡來的勇氣 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 130398}, {"id": 57127, "content": "不知道是过度自信还是自卑的表现", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 511352}, {"id": 57128, "content": "该内容成为该形式的毒药！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 55104}, {"id": 59436, "content": "再也不能好好的吃饭了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 521155}, {"id": 57648, "content": "曾经点进去看过一次，之后就果断卸载了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 445395}, {"id": 57137, "content": "妈的智障", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 511375}, {"id": 57138, "content": "还没看过直播的飘过～～～", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 486532}, {"id": 57139, "content": "呵呵哒", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 334924}, {"id": 57140, "content": "越来越不懂这个世界", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 503629}]}